Package org.neo4j.scheduler

Enum Group

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Group>
      • org.neo4j.scheduler.Group
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Group>
    public enum Group
extends Enum<Group>
    Represents a common group of jobs, defining how they should be scheduled.
